[In order to better assess the etiology of this foodborne cluster of
illness, it is important to know the kind of pies that are implicated,
the incubation period from ingestion of the alleged vehicle to onset
of symptoms and the length of illness. ProMED-mail awaits additional
information regarding this outbreak. - Mod.LL]

[Mexicali can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map
at http://healthmap.org/r/1owQ. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
